<subSubSection id="44911484C51ABD5BFF45F9245584F8BA" pageId="10" pageNumber="241" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="0C34470FC51ABD5BFF45F9245584F8BA" blockId="10.[151,1436,1492,1807]" pageId="10" pageNumber="241">
<emphasis id="3EFF9B1DC51ABD5BFF45F924502FF917" bold="true" box="[199,327,1672,1698]" pageId="10" pageNumber="241">Comment:</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="681A3AFEC51ABD5BFECCF924508CF916" author="Friese, H." box="[334,484,1672,1699]" pageId="10" pageNumber="241" pagination="19 - 22" refId="ref21977" refString="Friese, H. (1924) Neue formen der Bienengattungen Centris - Epicharis. Konowia, 3, 19 - 22." type="journal article" year="1924">Friese (1924)</bibRefCitation>
described this species as a variety of 
<taxonomicName id="CB8B3C8CC51ABD5BFC0BF92555CAF916" authority="(Perty, 1833)" baseAuthorityName="Perty" baseAuthorityYear="1833" box="[905,1186,1673,1699]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="241" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="moerens">
<emphasis id="3EFF9B1DC51ABD5BFC0BF92552F4F916" box="[905,924,1673,1699]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="241">C</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="3EFF9B1DC51ABD5BFC28F9255560F917" box="[938,1032,1673,1698]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="241">moerens</emphasis>
(Perty, 1833)
</taxonomicName>
, a member of the subgenus 
<emphasis id="3EFF9B1DC51ABD5BFF62F901519BF972" box="[224,243,1709,1735]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="241">C</emphasis>
. (
<emphasis id="3EFF9B1DC51ABD5BFE88F9005015F973" box="[266,381,1708,1734]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="241">Ptilotopus</emphasis>
). 
<bibRefCitation id="681A3AFEC51ABD5BFE17F901531AF972" author="Moure, J. S. &amp; Melo, G. A. R. &amp; Vivallo, F." box="[405,626,1708,1735]" pageId="10" pageNumber="241" pagination="83 - 142" refId="ref22678" refString="Moure, J. S., Melo, G. A. R. &amp; Vivallo, F. (2007) Centridini Cockerell &amp; Cockerell. In: Moure, J. S., Urban, D. &amp; Melo, G. A. R. (Eds.), Catalogue of Bees (Hymenoptera, Apoidea) in the Neotropical Region. Sociedade Brasileira de Entomologia, Curitiba, pp. 83 - 142." type="book chapter" year="2007">
Moure 
<emphasis id="3EFF9B1DC51ABD5BFE65F9015371F973" box="[487,537,1708,1734]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="241">et al</emphasis>
. (2007)
</bibRefCitation>
followed 
<bibRefCitation id="681A3AFEC51ABD5BFD66F9005213F972" author="Friese, H." box="[740,891,1708,1735]" pageId="10" pageNumber="241" pagination="19 - 22" refId="ref21977" refString="Friese, H. (1924) Neue formen der Bienengattungen Centris - Epicharis. Konowia, 3, 19 - 22." type="journal article" year="1924">Friese (1924)</bibRefCitation>
and cited it in that subgenus in the Catalogue of Bees in the Neotropical Region. The detailed study of the 
<typeStatus id="D330F9ADC51ABD5BFCB3F97C52FBF95F" box="[817,915,1744,1770]" pageId="10" pageNumber="241">holotype</typeStatus>
showed that 
<taxonomicName id="CB8B3C8CC51ABD5BFBAEF97D55D5F95F" authorityName="Friese" authorityYear="1924" box="[1068,1213,1744,1771]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="241" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flavicollis">
<emphasis id="3EFF9B1DC51ABD5BFBAEF97D5557F95E" box="[1068,1087,1745,1771]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="241">C</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="3EFF9B1DC51ABD5BFBCDF97C55D5F95F" box="[1103,1213,1744,1770]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="241">flavicollis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is a member of the subgenus 
<emphasis id="3EFF9B1DC51ABD5BFE84F9595071F8BA" box="[262,281,1781,1807]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="241">C</emphasis>
. (
<emphasis id="3EFF9B1DC51ABD5BFEB2F95850BAF8BB" box="[304,466,1780,1806]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="241">Melanocentris</emphasis>
) and not related to Perty’s species or with any other of 
<emphasis id="3EFF9B1DC51ABD5BFBBDF959553AF8BA" box="[1087,1106,1781,1807]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="241">C</emphasis>
. (
<emphasis id="3EFF9B1DC51ABD5BFBEBF95855B4F8BB" box="[1129,1244,1780,1806]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="241">Ptilotopus</emphasis>
).
</paragraph>
